A graduate from Memphis Academy of Arts, '''Ezra Tucker''' is an illustrator who won several awards, such as the ''Los Angeles Society of Illustrators'' ' gold medal. Tucker provided the artwork for [[William C. Dietz]]' novella ''[[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent]]''.

